WEBVTT

00:05:30.894 --> 00:05:33.306
Inawezekana majibu niliokua
nayo hayakua sawa,

00:05:33.330 --> 00:05:35.677
kua maswali yenyewe yalikua yamekosewa.

00:05:35.701 --> 00:05:39.263
Na sasa, palipokua mwanzoni
na mlima wa uhakika,

00:05:39.772 --> 00:05:42.583
palikua, ukishuka chini ya
chemchemi yake,

00:05:43.168 --> 00:05:44.721
bubujiko la mashaka,

00:05:45.691 --> 00:05:47.461
bubujiko lililoahidi mito.

00:05:48.357 --> 00:05:51.490
Ninaweza kufuatilia mchezo mzima wa maisha
yangu

00:05:51.514 --> 00:05:53.140
mpaka usiku ule kwenye lile kanisa

00:05:53.164 --> 00:05:55.246
pale mwokozi wangu hakuja kwa ajili yangu;

00:05:56.069 --> 00:05:58.591
pale kitu nilichoamini kwa hakika

00:05:59.328 --> 00:06:01.325
kikageuka kua, kama sio uongo,